---
title: Basil Pesto Chicken with Wilted Kale and Cannellini Beans
description: Pesto is a flavour packed sauce and here it transforms ordinary chicken breasts into a gorgeous plate! The creamy texture of the cannellini beans counter balances the tender wilted kale to bring together this bright and balanced dish.

